com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto

Interface ISyncTime


  • public interface ISyncTime
    A wrapper interface for synchronization times to isolate the client from changes in the storage format of those times.

    • Nested Class Summary

    • Field Detail

      • FACTORY

        static final ISyncTime.SyncTimeFactory FACTORY
        Factory used to create instances of ISyncTime

      • TIME_NONE

        static final ISyncTime TIME_NONE
        A time that can be used to specify that no time is desired/exists. No workspace/configuration/change history will ever have this value as its current time.

    • Method Detail

      • toString

        java.lang.String toString()
        Will return a string representation of this sync time. It is guaranteed that if 2 sync times are not equal, then the strings returned by their toString() methods will not be equal. Conversely, if 2 sync times are equal, then the strings returned by their toString() methods will be equal.
        Overrides:
        toString in class java.lang.Object

      • toSynchronizationTime

        ISynchronizationTime toSynchronizationTime()
        Will convert the receiver into an ISynchronizationTime suitable for transport.
